Glenwood swimmers participated in the non-company team race at Midmar on Saturday, 10 February. As part of their commitment to the community, they also represented the SA Legion. In addition Byron Goulder and Blaine Golden helped man the Legion table at the finish. Pictured at the event were: (back row) Luke van As, Karan Kota Raju, Joshua Jacoby, Tiago Cordeiro, Alex van Rooyen, Armand Nortje, Legionnaire Brian Dore, (front row) Kelly Geldenhuys, Byron Govender, Tracy McKay and Aaron Jacoby. The Midmar race was fun for all attendees, young and old. Pictured are some of the excited attendees, having fun in the sun. The Glenwood swimmers excitedly represented the SA Legion.